Mount the partitions
Install the base packages into /mnt (pacstrap /mnt base linux-zen linux-zen-headers linux-firmware git vim intel-ucode (or amd-ucode))
Generate the FSTAB file with genfstab -U /mnt >> /mnt/etc/FSTAB
Chroot in with arch-chroot /mnt

useradd -m  drew
echo "drew ALL=(ALL) ALL" >> /etc/sudoers.d/drew

